# Play-On-Words
Test program in development

Outline:
main()
	-DisplayScreen
		-scaleDisplay

	-RunGame
		-classDeck
		  -stack <card> //cards are now in a stack
			-newDeck() //initilize all letters
			-drawCard() //draw first card from top
			-shuffle() //randomize the stack
			-getTop() //flip the top cards of the 8 stacks

		-classPlayer
			-hand(cardList)()
			-words(listOfWords)()
			-createWord()
			-playerWord()
			-drawCard()
			
		-classCardList
			-addCard()
			-removeCard()
			-moveCard()
			-checkDictionary()
			-display()
			-card()

	-ImportDictionary

	-ExitGame
